query:
SELECT 
                        id as "id!",
                        market_id,
                        owner_id,
                        transaction_id,
                        NULL as "transaction_timestamp: _",
                        size as "size: _",
                        price as "price: _",
                        side as "side: Text<Side>"
                    FROM "order"
                    WHERE market_id = ?
                        AND side != ?
                        AND CAST(size AS REAL) > 0
                        AND CAST(price AS REAL) >= ?
                    ORDER BY CAST(price AS REAL) DESC, transaction_id
